{"tid":975792,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"商務部：中美就貿易問題和結構性問題進行廣泛、深入和細緻交流","createTime":"2019-01-10T02:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T03:07:26.000Z","uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0b43862573834c19e5c077d281351233c8862ae3","tid":975792,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://plib.aastocks.com/aafnnews/image/medialib/20180921145933377_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplib.aastocks.com%2Faafnnews%2Fimage%2Fmedialib%2F20180921145933377_m.jpg&h=e82ab725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據《新華社》報道，國家商務部發表聲明指，2018年1月7日至9日，中美雙方在北京舉行經貿問題副部級磋商。雙方積極落實兩國元首重要共識，就共同關注的貿易問題和結構性問題進行了廣泛、深入、細致的交流，增進了相互理解，為解決彼此關切問題奠定了基礎。雙方同意繼續保持密切聯繫。(lf/w)"},{"pid":"2e906d7bc2ed4003c96f230ef67a0944158b70d7","tid":975792,"uid":17429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:52:59.000Z","msg":"升"},{"pid":"a80162c3ec6ce94b7e9bc7545e818a0ca0a19d26","tid":975792,"uid":31773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:57:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係呢d空廢既說話"},{"pid":"66a11f2bc41a5cf89e518179c8ed6b18c4f4305b","tid":975792,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:58:32.000Z","msg":"又廣泛又深入，傾10年都傾唔完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1fde541ccdc36fad963cf2eae30994c2ddfe67","tid":975792,"uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:59:16.000Z","msg":"以講廢話黎講中國都算係國際上數一數二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打咁大篇野都係冇乜內容,真係冇乜人做到"},{"pid":"cc9dd15009155d0106e93722766cfbad1a658276","tid":975792,"uid":2078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"66a11f2bc41a5cf89e518179c8ed6b18c4f4305b","tid":975792,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:58:32.000Z","msg":"又廣泛又深入，傾1